  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 37-9-79, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REQUIRE EACH SCHOOL DISTRICT TO EMPLOY A LICENSED MENTAL HEALTH COUNSELOR IN EACH SCHOOL; TO REQUIRE ALL STUDENTS TO MEET WITH THEIR SCHOOL'S MENTAL HEALTH COUNSELOR AT LEAST ONCE PER SCHOOL YEAR; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
